{"tid":2056351,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「全民議政平台」十七區區議會最貼近下議院既時候","createTime":"2020-06-08T15:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T00:44:44.000Z","uid":149039,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d5a4441ca4b387009feb7fd5607f086e08c9844b","tid":2056351,"uid":149039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:20:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇人仲記得之攬炒巴拍過一條片</span> </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫區議會試下整外交議會/下議院<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果陣明明大家仲好熱血咁pub條片<br />\n依家明明就有人行緊呢條線 有人去整緊個雛形<br />\n點解國國安法過左之後<br />\n就冇人理十七區既全民議政平台！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個明明就係突破口！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢件事明明就係應該快刀斬亂麻咁過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n殺佢一個措手不及<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係 觀塘 灣仔 北區 油尖旺 呢啲地方唔肯即時過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係差我地呢啲小市民 去比壓力呢啲所謂既民主派！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地要人推一推先會肯行架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲落街去你果區既區議員辦事處/上佢地Facebook/IG<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同佢地講你支持全民議政平台啦！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要用佢哋重視既民意授權推佢地過呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算你果區過左都好 都不妨關心下件事 問下你果區既議員有咩幫到手 又或者搞下聯署支持！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要用民意 去證明我地都想要議政權利！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e353943688f31b37a46f6eb8b98b434bb8083f8","tid":2056351,"uid":149039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"153ce55c72a00cb16f6fd25b9bbc01fa66628437","tid":2056351,"uid":149039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:21:15.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"02db4930dbf99eb48054ef954366066163fdbca8","tid":2056351,"uid":149039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:21:25.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"0706c4897cf56a9c50cab69ec49f18358fdcec2d","tid":2056351,"uid":149039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:21:40.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"de93b361007e51fd8371e07e3cd1267d5091f25f","tid":2056351,"uid":149039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:21:51.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"9310f17891a6c5786ba409dc74de3f4dc372c6e6","tid":2056351,"uid":149039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:22:06.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"474245aa216561a86fecab3810baba3056d6a731","tid":2056351,"uid":149039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:22:21.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"314b47e143495a9c494e68b05d7ddbcef4d903e0","tid":2056351,"uid":149039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:22:50.000Z","msg":"兩個3添 自膠Sor<br />\n6"},{"pid":"5e8ea2e0708f36c85dbb793ac34cafc6fc7a9785","tid":2056351,"uid":149039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:23:03.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"0827963c219f43e9b18c4c2496f8920372090645","tid":2056351,"uid":149039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:23:14.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"f36d24f091c9a9c92c2b450b3ba79c1c2171694e","tid":2056351,"uid":149039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T15:23:28.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"d3afaf1fd8